model.metaheuristic.utils.solutionattribute

Class SolutionAttribute<S extends Solution<?>,V>

  • java.lang.Object
    • model.metaheuristic.utils.solutionattribute.SolutionAttribute<S,V>
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    CrowdingDistance, DominanceRanking, Generation, LocationAttribute, NumberOfViolatedConstraints, OverallConstraintViolation, StrengthRawFitness

    public class SolutionAttribute<S extends Solution<?>,V>
extends Object
    Generic class for implementing SolutionAttribute classes. By default, the identifier of a SolutionAttribute is the class object, but it can be set to a different value when constructing an instance.
